trans-unit.source: Provides a set of initialization methods for instances of the <see cref="T:System.Collections.Immutable.ImmutableStack`1" /> class.

trans-unit.source: This type is thread safe.
trans-unit.target: Данный тип потокобезопасен.

trans-unit.source: The type of items to be stored in the immutable stack.
